title: Johnny Cash - The Original Sun Sound of Johnny Cash [FLAC]
description:
From Wikipedia:

The Original Sun Sound is the eighteenth overall studio album by singer Johnny Cash and was released by Sun Records in 1964.


Track listing

"Always Alone" (T. Daffan)
"Country Boy" (J. Cash)
"Goodnight Irene" (H. Ledbetter/J. "Superslim" Lomax III)
"Wide Open Road" (J. Cash)
"Thanks a Lot" (C. Rich)
"Big River" (J. Cash)
"Belshazar" (J. Cash)
"Born to Lose" (F. Brown)
"New Mexico" (aka "Trail to Mexico") (Public Domain)
"I Forgot to Remember to Forget" (C. Feathers/S. Kesler)
"Two Timin' Woman" (C. Snow)
"Story of a Broken Heart" (S. Phillips)
